name: Eve 4.19 (2016/21)
description:
This digital image is based on my watercolor work from eve series. The eve series of paintings explore issues beyond the body alone and could be considered existential. I got interest in Carl Jung's school of analytical psychology, which highlights a dual concept of feminine inner personality in the unconscious mind of a man and a masculine inner personality in the unconscious mind of a woman. The interpretations process is taken through direct observation during dialogue with model. I try to understand alter perceptions through the dipiction of several angle.
